<Layout
	title="About Spokdom"
	description="Spokdom publishes honest, hands-on reviews and comparisons of AI tools and SaaS apps to help you pick the right software faster."
	pubDate={new Date('June 18 2026')}
>
	<p>
		<strong>Spokdom</strong> is a review site for people who are tired of guessing which software to
		use. New AI tools and SaaS apps launch every week — we test them, compare the realistic
		alternatives, break down the pricing, and tell you which one actually fits your use case.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every review aims to answer one question: <em>should you use this, and if not, what should you
		use instead?</em> We focus on practical comparisons — "X vs Y", "best tools for Z", pricing and
		plan breakdowns, and alternatives to the popular options — so you can decide in minutes, not
		hours.
	</p>

	<p>
		<strong>How we make money.</strong> Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you sign up
		through them, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. It never changes our verdict —
		we recommend the tool that wins, not the one that pays.
	</p>

	<p>
		The site runs as a fast, static website and is updated regularly. Have a tool you want reviewed?
		Let us know.
	</p>
</Layout>
